| image1 = Vandalized ticket gates in Fanling station.jpg | caption1 = 粉嶺站遭受破壞的閘機
| image2 = Replaced ticket gates in Fanling station.jpg | caption2 = 粉嶺站閘機遭受破壞後的替代閘機
| image3 = Vandalized information kiosk in Fanling station.jpg | caption3 = 粉嶺站遭受破壞的客務中心
